{"body": "\r\n\"1) This implementation is not performatic. To each unique record in the table it perform a new query to get the groups.\"\r\n\r\nThis is similar to find_in_batches, it also has a new query to get each batch, it returns array as batch, this would return Relation, hence no query fired unless user calls all, first etc\r\n\r\n\"2) I don't see many applications using this code.\", \r\n\r\nyou might be right, \r\n\r\nI hope applications may use it and it will get enhanced\r\nhttp://stackoverflow.com/questions/2432412/group-by-country-with-activerecords-in-rails and related\r\n\r\nanyways thanks @rafaelfranca \r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/11692483", "created_at": "2012-12-26T19:24:16Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8611#issuecomment-11692483", "updated_at": "2012-12-26T19:24:16Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8611, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/amolpujari", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/860ef9f1f54410fcfb2eff1b5f111e44?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Ff3b677a28135afae45de44314f185447.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari/received_events", "gravatar_id": "860ef9f1f54410fcfb2eff1b5f111e44", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "amolpujari", "type": "User", "id": 840214, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amolpujari/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f1a0bd3543c15100a494"}, "i